window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b>Neuromancer</b> is the multiple award-winning novel that launched the astonishing career of William Gibson. The first fully-realized glimpse of humankind's digital future, it is a shocking vision that has challenged our assumptions about our technology and ourselves, reinvented the way we speak and think, and forever altered the landscape of our imaginations.<p>Now, for the first time, Ace Books is proud to present this groundbreaking literary achievement in a trade paperback edition.</p>"; 
